{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"btuc7d44v7v0qbckp5a7sq7","title":"How to Build Habits in 4 Simple Steps","desc":"","updated":1654284769936,"created":1654246866047,"custom":{},"fname":"books.atomic-habits.the-fundamentals.how-to-build-habits-in-4-simple-steps","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Public"},"contentHash":"0ed35a712dc3d74ca342f9659110ef08","links":[{"from":{"fname":"books.atomic-habits.the-fundamentals","vaultName":"Public"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":39,"offset":272},"end":{"line":5,"column":118,"offset":351},"indent":[]},"value":"books.atomic-habits.the-fundamentals.how-to-build-habits-in-4-simple-steps"}],"anchors":{"why-your-brain-builds-haabits":{"type":"header","text":"Why Your Brain Builds Haabits","value":"why-your-brain-builds-haabits","line":8,"column":0,"depth":3},"the-science-of-how-habits-work":{"type":"header","text":"The Science of how Habits work","value":"the-science-of-how-habits-work","line":10,"column":0,"depth":3},"the-4-laws-of-behavior-change":{"type":"header","text":"The 4 Laws of Behavior Change","value":"the-4-laws-of-behavior-change","line":18,"column":0,"depth":3},"chapter-summary":{"type":"header","text":"Chapter Summary","value":"chapter-summary","line":31,"column":0,"depth":3}},"children":[],"parent":"pacsqekn5errnah0lqla72r","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"how-to-build-habits-in-4-simple-steps\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#how-to-build-habits-in-4-simple-steps\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>How to Build Habits in 4 Simple Steps</h1>\n<h3 id=\"why-your-brain-builds-haabits\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#why-your-brain-builds-haabits\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Why Your Brain Builds Haabits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>habit is a behavior that has been repeated enough times to become automatic</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"the-science-of-how-habits-work\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#the-science-of-how-habits-work\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>The Science of how Habits work</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>What you want - get money, be rich, good teeth</li>\n<li>Craving\n<ol>\n<li>the goal: you dont want to smoke a cigarette but you want the buzz, you don't care about brushing your teeth but you want a clean mouth</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>Response\n<ol>\n<li>brush teeth, get job, etc.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>Reward\n<ol>\n<li>the craving</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"the-4-laws-of-behavior-change\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#the-4-laws-of-behavior-change\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>The 4 Laws of Behavior Change</h3>\n<p>Create a good Habit</p>\n<ol>\n<li>(Cue) Make it obvious</li>\n<li>(Craving ) Make it attractive</li>\n<li>(Response) Make it easy</li>\n<li>(Reward) Make it satisfying</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Break a bad habit:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>(Cue) Make it invisible</li>\n<li>(Craving) Make it ugly</li>\n<li>(Response) Make it difficult</li>\n<li>(Reward) Make it unsatisfying</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"chapter-summary\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#chapter-summary\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Chapter Summary</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Purpose of habits is to solve problems with as little energy and effort as possible</li>\n<li>Make it obvious, make it attractive, make it easy make it satisfying</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Notes/notes/pacsqekn5errnah0lqla72r\">The Fundamentals (Public)</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"nvix4le1j3rae1dzsb81q5l","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1654192376926,"created":1654192376926,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note"